Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:32.07,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}潛力越高 麻煩越大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:37.56,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}dropout mentality 凌駕於非日常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:42.30,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我們帶著一臉睡意
