Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.91,0:21:46.17,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}太陽が射す 閉ざした瞼の裏側に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:55.45,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}赤い残像を 革の鞄にノートとペンを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.88,0:21:58.31,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}さあ 歩き出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:06.61,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}描いても描いても 綺麗にならない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:12.14,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}選んだ絵の具に 罪は無い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.82,0:22:19.02,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}昨日の夜中に 見た流れ星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.21,0:22:22.76,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}まだ覚えている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:25.95,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}I was waiting for
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.49,0:22:31.66,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}Hello,Shooting-Star Hello,Shooting-Star again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:37.74,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}待っていたよ 夢を見るあの子はずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.31,0:22:49.87,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}ここにいるの あの日のまま
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.25,0:22:52.64,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}また光って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:20.10,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.91,0:21:46.17,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}當那一道陽光 在緊閉的雙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:55.45,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}投下赤紅的殘像 把本子和筆收進書包
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.88,0:21:58.31,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}然後走出教室
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:06.61,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}畫過一幅又一幅 筆下的風景卻如此平凡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:12.14,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我知道選擇的顏料 並沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.82,0:22:19.02,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}昨天夜深人靜時 撞進心裡的那顆流星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.21,0:22:22.76,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}現在還閃耀在記憶裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:25.95,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我一直在等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.49,0:22:31.66,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}你好 流星 你好 流星 又見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:37.74,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我一直在等 當年那個做夢的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.31,0:22:49.87,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}一直在這裡 時間停止在那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.25,0:22:52.64,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}只希望看到你再閃耀一次
